      <data key="d4">["3"]</data>
      <data key="d7">Top track in Cumulus pipeline diagram; NICE data ingestion and structuring; unclear if Cumulus plans full entity extraction from guidelines; Mediha had done Cypher query / graph work on guidelines</data>
