      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "we need someone from the clinical team to look into the cases and literally highlight and tell us each entity ... we need to define the tool that we're going to use in order for them to be able to do those entity annotations", "ts": 660, "source": "chapter_2"}]</data>
      <data key="d4">["2"]</data>
      <data key="d7">Must meet data privacy requirements; may pre-populate using AI to reduce clinical team effort; several tools exist</data>
