    <node id="topic:rules-representation">
      <data key="d0">Topic</data>
      <data key="d1">Rules Representation (Cypher Queries vs Graphs)</data>
      <data key="d2">0.9</data>
      <data key="d3">[{"quote": "We can either make them as cipher queries or do them as graphs. Now, the cipher queries is like an intermediate step to get to graphs.", "ts": 1490, "source": "chapter_3"}]</data>
