      <data key="d28">["2", "2"]</data>
      <data key="d29">Brendan's patent document (Ch2), which describes the full system and breaks it into modules including entity identification and pseudonymization, provides the conceptual foundation and entity-type reference that ground truth annotation work will need to operationalise</data>
      <data key="d27">{"source_quote": {"quote": "compare it back to the patent, that Brendan's patent document, and he had that description of like the whole system, then we had broken it down into different modules", "ts": 790, "chapter": "2", "speaker": "Laura Gongas"}, "target_quote": {"quote": "we want to evaluate how they're doing with this pseudonymization ... we need to have annotations or like countries so they can compare what they predicted versus what it should actually be", "ts": 565, "chapter": "2", "speaker": "Laura Gongas"}}</data>
