      <data key="d28">["2", "3"]</data>
      <data key="d29">Mediha's graph database work (Ch2, presented at Sprint 9) provides the concrete artefact that grounds the Ch3 rules representation discussion (Cypher queries as intermediate step toward the graph)</data>
